name: Wire Bracelet Set
description: Set of 4 pearl, silver, and gold wire bracelets to mix and match with our handmade bangles.

name: Handmade Bangles
description:
**These are extremely popular!! More options will be available in 4 weeks. We have about 20 bangles left. Please email us if you are interested - SEE INSTRUCTIONS BELOW! Please do not put these items in your shopping cart. We will send you an invoice once we get in contact with you. Thank you!!**

Handmade proudly in the USA! 

All the bracelets are made with hand selected semiprecious stones: smokey quartz, Lava stones, shells, turquoise, jade, coral, and many more natural stones all wrapped with gold plated wire.

Because each bangle is one-of-a-kind... it's best to email us so we can contact you with stone options. 

Please email shop.gnome.adic@gmail.com (or use the "contact us" page), and please include ALL of the following information: 

1) Hand Size: Small, Medium, Large *This is important when sliding bangle on**
2) Wrist size: Small, Medium, Large
3) Stone Colors you like: (neutrals, colors (if so which colors), pearls, coins, etc.) 
4) How many would you want to stack? (2, 3, 4 or 5?)

Once we receive your email, we will send you options, you select your bangles, and we will send you an invoice. Hooray! That's it!

**Each bangle fits differently due to the size of the natural stones.**

name: Boot Leg Warmers
description:
Super comfy and stylish leg/boot warmers are the newest trend this season! Wear them over your skinnys and either over or under your boots. They can easily be pulled up to your knee, or scrunch them down to your liking.

Flip them upside down and wear the lace around your ankle to doll up your heels and flats while keeping your shins and ankles warm!

But don't wait long... these sell out very quickly!

These boot warmers come embellished with lace and buttons.

name: Boot Socks
description:
Girly knee high boot socks! These open knit, diamond pattern socks have been embellished with ivory lace and buttons. They are super stretchy, one size fits most.

They Measure 23 inches long and the cuff will stretch to fit up to an 18 inch calf, fitting most women shoe sizes 6-10 comfortably.

Made from 100% Cotton
Hand wash. Lay flat to dry

name: Signature Bird Necklace
description:
By far this necklace is our most popular! If you are looking for a gift, you can not go wrong with this beautiful piece. Each necklace is hand-made with 14K gold-fill or sterling silver, freshwater pearls, and brass elements.

17" Long. 1.25" Drop.

Please choose your 14k gold-fill or sterling silver selection below.

name: Signature Bird Earrings
description:
Our signature sparrows in a pair of earrings. How perfect! These have been found on the ears of many bridal parties, mother of the brides, and happy customers!

Each pair of earrings is handmade with sterling silver, freshwater pearls and vintage brass elements. 1.75" drop. 

Please choose your 14k gold-fill or sterling silver selection below.

name: Signature Bee Necklace
description:
A beautiful variation of our signature sparrow necklace. Each necklace is handmade with sterling silver, 14k gold-fill, freshwater pearls and vintage brass stampings. 

16" Long. 

Available in gold-fill or sterling silver.

name: Treasured Pebbles Necklace
description:
Like tiny treasured pebbles. Choose from either a freshwater seed pearl or a tiny crystal. Each necklace is handmade with sterling silver or 14 kt. gold-fill and freshwater pearls or swarovski crystal. 

Standard chain length: 15" Long. 

We can make the chain longer if requested. Lengthening the chain  is $5.00. Just add the appropriate chain length to the cart.

name: Story Book Earrings
description:
Each pair is handmade with sterling silver wires, vintage brass stamped branches, silver plated birds, and a semi-precious carved flower. 2" Long.

Flower is available in: Ocean (Pictured), Cream, Sunset(Berry), or Pear (Lime Green).

name: Faithful Friend Necklace
description:
